Random fact for those who might not know (Spoilers for Fate/Stay Night, but no more than the doujin itself): This is based on an actual Bad End of Fate/Stay Night, the numerically last one, Number 40, titled Femme Fatale. It is achieved by choosing not to finish off Saber Alter at the very end of Heaven's Feel, as shown in the beginning of the story here. However, in the real Bad End, Sakura used penis shaped worms, not tentacles, and it happens off screen. Amusingly, the games hint corner earlier tells you that the final Bad End is a harem ending. As this doujin shows, that is sort of true, if you stretch the definition of a "harem ending" a bit.
TL;DR: This is a mostly canon event in one of the largest media franchises in the world, at least in a Bad End.
